<p>
<note type="mod" resp="#resp2" n="0907007" target="#nkr_note_mod_0907007">國【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note resp="#resp2" n="0907008" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0907008">居士【大】，優婆塞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note type="mod" resp="#resp2" n="0907009" target="#nkr_note_mod_0907009">白【大】，真【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0908001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0908001">輜【大】，轒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
